      <h1>Moo<br/><span>(Mosaic)</span></h1>
      <h3>Product definition, research, testing &amp; prototyping</h3>
      <h2>I worked with the Heads of Tech and Product at Moo for three months to help discover what the digital business card could be. When I arrived, they had little more than a few sketches from their initial meetings, and I helped them get to an alpha product to test with potential users.</h2>

    
